						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/Berlin"
					},
					"body": "[~bhouse] Ah ok, I thought it should work this way too:\r\n{code}\r\n<Alloy>\r\n\t<NavigationWindow>\r\n\t\t<TabGroup title=\"Tabgroup\">\r\n\t\t\t<Tab title=\"tab\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<Window/>\r\n\t\t\t</Tab>\r\n\t\t\t<Tab title=\"tab\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<Window/>\r\n\t\t\t</Tab>\r\n\t\t</TabGroup>\r\n\t</NavigationWindow>\r\n</Alloy>\r\n{code}\r\nand now when you open a new window it should still display the bottom navigation. But you want to have the NavigationWindow inside the Tabs. ",
